      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need to talk to someone about something weird. i think i'm seeing things before they actually happen. like, i saw this specific cracked coffee mug in a window today and immediately after i saw a headline about a major bridge collapse. it wasn't a coincidence i could feel it. has this ever happened to anyone else or am i actually losing it?",
